      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-loved, looks great, and runs like a dream. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is totally ready for its next adventure. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
