      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 540i Sedan finished in Sophisto Grey Metallic. This vehicle represents a well-preserved example of German engineering, showing only the expected signs of careful use. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving. Inside, the Black Dakota leather upholstery is supple, free of tears or significant bolster wear, and the cabin remains a smoke-free environment. All technological features, including the iDrive 6.0 system, gesture control, and the Harman Kardon surround sound, function perfectly. Mechanically, the 3.0L TwinPower Turbo inline-six runs smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service record from authorized dealerships. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service, brake pad replacement, and a set of Michelin Pilot Sport tires with approximately 80% tread remaining. The undercarriage is clean, and the 19-inch M-Sport wheels are free of curb rash. This car offers a balanced blend of performance and luxury for the discerning driver who values a documented history and mechanical integrity.",
